{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_52_03",
  "title": "成宮すず 3話 おたのもうします",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――舞妓さんのイベント会場",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Apprentice geisha Event Venue",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1199.9999762,
          "startTime": 1.1999999762
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "なんてこと……舞妓さん、優雅ですわ……\n綺麗に揃った指先……物憂げな表情がたまりませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a thing… the apprentice geisha is so elegant…\nThose beautifully aligned fingertips… that melancholic expression is irresistible!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、綺麗だな\n東京ではこういうイベントはあまりないから新鮮だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ she's beautiful.\nEvents like this are rare in Tokyo‚ so it's refreshing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9666672389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.5882652998
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "舞妓さんは修業中の身と言っていましたわよね\nそれなのにあの色気……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said apprentice geishas are in training‚ right?\nAnd yet that allure…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4000005722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1221194346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "どうすれば、あんなに色気を出せるんでしょうか……\n……とにもかくにも、まずは実践ですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How can one exude such allure…\n…In any case‚ practice comes first!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6333339055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "じ、実践……？\n何をする気なんだ、すず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-practice…?\nWhat are you planning to do‚ Suzu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5666672389,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4399.999427799998,
          "startTime": 42.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4321265459
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.4321265459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "少し歩いたら喉が渇いたな。すず、何か飲むか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got thirsty after walking a bit. Suzu‚ want something to drink?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.08212502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4852994044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "はい。{user}はん\n私はあのお抹茶が飲みたい……どす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ {user}-han.\nI want to drink that matcha… dosu!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.266665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.9846117417
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……どす？　……あ、ああ、抹茶だな\n甘いお茶菓子とかも一緒に売ってるみたいだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Dosu? …Ah‚ right‚ matcha.\nIt looks like they also sell sweets for tea…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.066665713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.2838120222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "おおきに、{user}はん\nでは、あの桜の形のお茶菓子もおたのもうします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am grateful‚ {user}-han.\nThen‚ I shall also request of those cherry blossom-shaped sweets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1666601181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.2340205907
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、すず。さっきから、どうしたんだ？\nなんだか、言葉遣いが変……というか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ Suzu. What's gotten into you?\nYour way of speaking is strange… or rather…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3999934514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.9287600278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、やっと気付きはりましたか！　私、どうしたら\n舞妓さんのように色気を身につけられるか考えましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ you finally noticed! I thought about how\nI could acquire charm like apprentice geishas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9999934514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.4506138245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "私の鋭い洞察力で、舞妓さんのあの上品な喋り方が\n重要だと気付きましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With my sharp insight‚ I realized that the apprentice geisha's\nelegant way of speaking is important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5666601181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.9813633997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "元々成宮家の令嬢かつ二代目星降る奇跡として気品\n溢れる私でしたが、さらに上品になれた気がしますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a young lady of the Narumiya family and the \"Second Miracle of Falling Stars\"‚\nI'm already graceful‚ but I feel I've become even more refined.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.0999934514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2075921773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "鬼に金棒、成宮すずに京ことば！\nさらなる高みへ上り詰めますわ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like an oni with an iron club— Suzu Narumiya with Kyoto dialect!\nI'll climb to even greater heights…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5333267848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.7116753021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……言葉遣いだけ真似しても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Even if you only imitate the way of speaking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7116753021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.3431487003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "何か言いましたどす！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you say something‚ dosu!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3431487003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.4217483041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや。勉強熱心なのはいいことなんだが……\nなんというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no. Being studious is a good thing‚ but…\nHow should I put it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4355261005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、いいですわ。で、どうどす？\n心なしか大人っぽく見えてきたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's fine. So‚ how is it‚ dosu?\nDon't I look somewhat more mature…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.466660118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "大人っぽく……そうだな……\nうーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mature… well…\nHmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4710906714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.21219875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "なんですの、その間は\n何か言いたいことがあるんどすか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's with that pause?\nDo you have something you want to say‚ dosu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.7333339055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.4816226003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺はすずはすずのままでいいと思うぞ\n無理に舞妓さんの真似をしなくても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you are fine just being yourself‚ Suzu.\nYou don't need to force yourself to imitate apprentice geishas…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1333410263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.9261124608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それより、舞踊のしなやかさをダンスに取り入れるとか\n気遣いの姿勢を見習うとか、他にも方法はあるだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather‚ you could incorporate the gracefulness of traditional dance into your dancing‚\nor learn from their considerate attitude. There are other ways‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.2666743596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうですが、何事も形から入ることは重要ですわ\nでも……確かに一理ありますわね",
      "translations": {
